    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, ideal for someone seeking a major project or a source for parts. The engine currently does not run, and there are significant rust issues throughout the frame and body panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the electronics are largely non-functional. Expect to put in substantial work or use it to keep another vehicle on the road.",
